                "invention-title": [
                    "Methanol and hydrogen mixed combustion device",
                    "一种甲醇氢气混合燃烧装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a methanol and hydrogen mixed combustion device which comprises a combustion device body, the combustion device body comprises a boiler body and a mixed connector piece, the mixed connector piece is installed on the boiler body and provides hot air for the boiler body, a plurality of heating water pipes are installed in the boiler body, a water inlet pipe is installed at one end of the boiler body, and a water outlet pipe is installed at the other end of the boiler body; cold water is supplied into the boiler body through the water inlet pipe, then mixed gas supplied by the mixed connector piece is ignited, the mixed gas comprises methyl alcohol, air and hydrogen, the methyl alcohol and the air are made to be combusted easily instead of being not prone to combustion after being input, and the flowing speed of the air can be increased through a high-power draught fan. By means of the structure, flowing of hot air in the boiler body can be greatly improved, then cold water in the water inlet pipe is rapidly heated, heated hot water can be supplied outwards through the water outlet pipe, the effect that the hot water can be used immediately after being heated can be well achieved, and the size of the device is much smaller than that of an existing boiler."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种甲醇氢气混合燃烧装置，包括：燃烧装置主体，该燃烧装置主体包括锅炉体、混合接头件，混合接头件安装在锅炉体上，为锅炉体提供热空气，而锅炉体内安装有多个加热水管，在锅炉体的一端安装有进水管，另一端安装有出水管，进水管向锅炉体内供入冷水，而后点燃混合接头件供入的混合气体，混合气体包括甲醇、空气、氢气，使得甲醇和空气在输入后从不易燃烧变成了轻易燃烧，空气可以通过大功率的风机提高空气的流动速度，可以大大提高热空气在锅炉体的流动，进而对进水管内的冷水进行快速加热，加热的热水则可以通过出水管向外供水，可以较好的做到即热即用的效果，使得该装置在体型上也比现有的锅炉要小很多。"
                }
            ]
